## Version Management

### Endpoint Versioning
- **Use clear version indicators** in summaries (e.g., "v1", "v2 (beta)")
- **Maintain backward compatibility** when possible
- **Document version differences** in descriptions
- **Use consistent version formatting** (lowercase "v1", "v2")

